__get (line 110)

Make accessing some individual elements of the feed easier.

Special accessors 'entry' and 'entries' are provided so that if you wish to iterate over an Atom feed's entries, you can do so using foreach ($feed->entries as $entry) or foreach ($feed->entry as $entry).

  • access: public
mixed __get (string $var)
  • string $var: The property to access.
Redefinition of:
Zend_Gdata_App_Base::__get()
Magic getter to allow acces like $entry->foo to call $entry->getFoo() Alternatively, if no getFoo() is defined, but a $_foo protected variable is defined, this is returned.
Redefined in descendants as:
  • Zend_Gdata_App_Feed::__get() : Make accessing some individual elements of the feed easier.
